text: Kudushlibashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Starokurmashevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 56 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 10 km from Kushnarenkovo, 3 km from Starokurmashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Kudushlibashevo
